### Create a valid booking
POST http://localhost:8082/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-1",
  "flightId": "SK101",
  "totalAmount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "passengers": [
    {
      "firstName": "Asha",
      "lastName": "Rao",
      "dateOfBirth": "1998-03-15",
      "passportNumber": "A1234567",
      "email": "asha.rao@example.com"
    }
  ]
}

### Trigger overbooking error
POST http://localhost:8082/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-1",
  "flightId": "FULL",
  "totalAmount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "passengers": [
    {
      "firstName": "Asha",
      "lastName": "Rao",
      "dateOfBirth": "1998-03-15",
      "passportNumber": "A1234567",
      "email": "asha.rao@example.com"
    }
  ]
}

### Trigger passenger validation error
POST http://localhost:8082/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-1",
  "flightId": "SK101",
  "totalAmount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "passengers": [
    {
      "firstName": "",
      "lastName": "Rao",
      "dateOfBirth": "2030-03-15",
      "passportNumber": "bad",
      "email": "not-an-email"
    }
  ]
}

### Get bookings for a user
GET http://localhost:8082/api/bookings?userId=user-1

### Get one booking
GET http://localhost:8082/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}

### Confirm a pending booking
PATCH http://localhost:8082/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/confirm

### Mark payment failed
PATCH http://localhost:8082/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/payment-failed

### Cancel a pending or failed booking
PATCH http://localhost:8082/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel
